gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Raptors 123, Hawks 121
gameRecap.excerpt: The Raptors defeated the Hawks, 123-121. Immanuel Quickley recorded 24 points, seven rebounds, and five assists for the Raptors, with Scottie Barnes adding 20 points, 10 assists, and five rebounds in the victory. Dejounte Murray tallied 24 points, 10 rebounds, and seven assists for the Hawks in the losing effort. The Raptors improve to 21-36, while the Hawks fall to 24-32.
